{"tid":1118450,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"仆佢個街天后嗰間龍鳳冰室","createTime":"2019-04-21T12:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T13:37:32.000Z","uid":77251,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0243dff711930ddbe773cfbb333d644e03b172","tid":1118450,"uid":77251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:14:24.000Z","msg":"今朝叫條仔落去買咗個早餐<br />\n買咗個早餐加3蚊菠蘿包轉菠蘿油<br />\n點知返到去打開個外賣發現係菠蘿包<br />\n頭先夜晚落街買外賣 順便諗住去攞返個三蚊<br />\n仆佢個街唔肯退喎 又話咩唔係早班同事唔清楚<br />\n又話咩點解唔拎返落嚟即刻換 <br />\n我屌啦 平時lunch time係車仔麵鋪買外賣畀少咗餸咪又係放工去車仔麵舖攞返個餸錢<br />\n仆你個街每個月賺成幾十萬 三蚊都唔肯退<br />\n正契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282dc332e2d039c3c462fd1c28720e299080eadb","tid":1118450,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"你有冇證據俾佢睇先"},{"pid":"fd7e9042c51deea6f0e9470c21bb9f073c9e2660","tid":1118450,"uid":77251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"282dc332e2d039c3c462fd1c28720e299080eadb","tid":1118450,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"你有冇證據俾佢睇先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T12:25:02.000Z","msg":"攞外賣會擺低張單"},{"pid":"73ecd7be3b7a99f4342dee3a70b12d678ae6c28c","tid":1118450,"uid":77092,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:27:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7e752016e73c3e0931d605ad1c0b5d5498a382e","tid":1118450,"uid":29070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:28:28.000Z","msg":"係咪林子善條仆街開嗰間？"},{"pid":"5546389e9bb677a5d3eb724e6cc29e1d74980288","tid":1118450,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:33:18.000Z","msg":"早餐食寶湖"},{"pid":"05bd4bda64d32b0622dabe74550e2112a403a537","tid":1118450,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T13:34:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd61adb80733e0eb0f8adefa0ad92486668c0c9a","tid":1118450,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s